    question: '<h3>How much do you know about HTML character entities?</h3>\n<p>If you have a webpage called “black&#x26;white”, what character entity is best to use in the following URL:</p>\n<p><code>&#x3C;a href="?page=black???white&#x26;action=view">Link to B/W&#x3C;/a></code></p>\n',
